  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/eee0a84813222c2e1f7fac2d2c759f3e.avif?t=1750118506\" width=610 height=180 /></span><br><br>Using your puzzle-solving skills, guide all mummies through various chambers full of traps to finally set them free from the evil Pharaoh Cléo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to help these Mummies escape:</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Control all the Mummies together, that is, by moving them in a certain direction, they all will too.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/c71bf56f475fe0d58b81962382fd069b.poster.avif?t=1750118506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/c71bf56f475fe0d58b81962382fd069b.webm?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/c71bf56f475fe0d58b81962382fd069b.mp4?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Make sure that each mummy takes the corresponding staff before going to the Totem of the same color, as this is the only way the Portal will open.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/61a551c938907e6af59f2077187397f1.poster.avif?t=1750118506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/61a551c938907e6af59f2077187397f1.webm?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/61a551c938907e6af59f2077187397f1.mp4?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><u><strong> Take care with:</strong></u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Holes: It is death for sure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/71635475703dbfbe4d1aeb23ba2c296e.poster.avif?t=1750118506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/71635475703dbfbe4d1aeb23ba2c296e.webm?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/71635475703dbfbe4d1aeb23ba2c296e.mp4?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Spears: It is not good to be pricked!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/9d84e6903c6c73537edc3be6d9d23507.poster.avif?t=1750118506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/9d84e6903c6c73537edc3be6d9d23507.webm?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/9d84e6903c6c73537edc3be6d9d23507.mp4?t=1750118506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br></li><li><u><strong> Keep an eye:</strong></u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Broken Floor: Nothing can happen, but be careful!<br></li><li> Magic Mist: Get the crown, otherwise the cumin will be uncertain and the end almost certain.<br></li><li> Mud: She will delay you, but it can help you.</li></ul></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593410/extras/05e5eddde03032e55a7a206ca5b61323.avif?t=1750118506\" width=610 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMPATIBLE WITH THE NEW TILT FIVE ™ AUGMENTED REALITY SYSTEM!</h2><br><br>For the Tilt Five™ system, modifications designed to improve immersion in the game have been added, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Increased intensity and height of particle effects;<br></li><li> Positioning the scenery below the board, giving the feeling of playing inside a real chamber of an Egyptian pyramid;<br></li><li> Use the Wand to control mummies, allowing the player to select the direction and the mummies will move according to the player's vision.</li></ul>",
